### Health check
GET http://localhost:5071/

### Get file from GitLab (example)
### Format: /group/project/-/raw/ref/file_path
GET http://localhost:5071/arch/components/-/raw/main/person-customer.iuml

### Get README.md from root of repository
GET http://localhost:5071/mygroup/myproject/-/raw/main/README.md

### Get file from subdirectory
GET http://localhost:5071/mygroup/myproject/-/raw/main/src/Program.cs

### Get file with special characters in path
GET http://localhost:5071/mygroup/myproject/-/raw/main/config/appsettings.json

### Get file from different branch
GET http://localhost:5071/mygroup/myproject/-/raw/develop/README.md

### Get file from tag
GET http://localhost:5071/mygroup/myproject/-/raw/v1.0.0/CHANGELOG.md

### Get file from subgroup (nested groups)
GET http://localhost:5071/group/subgroup/project/-/raw/main/file.txt

### Error case: file not found
GET http://localhost:5071/mygroup/myproject/-/raw/main/nonexistent.txt

### Error case: invalid format (missing -/raw)
GET http://localhost:5071/mygroup/myproject/main/README.md

### Error case: project not found
GET http://localhost:5071/invalid/project/-/raw/main/README.md
